g/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1fbda0c7d3c31aaf22f76d49dd2f52ee9c6abc","tid":776262,"uid":17510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"認真  天下 圍攻香港立法會<br />\n<br />\n依個係一個極好契機去爭取普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原因<br />\n<br />\n1   立法會制度同法國當年既三級議會好似<br />\n班功能組別、保皇黨根本就唔洗睇選民面色做人<br />\n<br />\n搞出咁大壇野仲否決引用特權法<br />\n草菅人命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2  支那比美國製裁到成隻烏龜咁<br />\n而家連自己既假想敵 日本，都唔敢得罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圍堵支那既島鏈隨著北韓投誠經已完成<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔趁而家參與圍堵支那仲等幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獨立良機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26077245245e87faea75e368f6fee574542128f","tid":776262,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c45d18802d7f918f6c49fc357b0a8fd2e1e08e","tid":776262,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c893d9d8e04a93e5a5af3a0cbbac3e4e5d53bde3","tid":776262,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T10:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保皇狗打手民主黨擁躉唔敢入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0833e97a42c881feffb5f887457852f661e864","tid":776262,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T03:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90a6725c7e7d71605ef546ff7bb354177ef38dd","tid":776262,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T03:59:58.000Z","msg":"保皇狗打手關愛座hunter<br />\n寧願推泛民舊聞都唔敢入來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"